<div class="home-container">
 <div class="home-welcome-wrapper">
  
  <div class="home-header">
   <h3> Welcome to stratMap v0.4</h3>
  </div>
  
  <div class="home-description">

   <p> The purpose of this application is to automatically generate 
   a stratigraphic column based on the information you provide.  Furthermore,
   the application is capable of plotting the columns on a map and displaying the
   generated columns and corresponding data on an easily accessible window panel.
   </p>
   </br>
   <p>For information about version changes, visit the <a href="https://github.com/arac-codespace/strat-map">Github repository</a>.</p>
   </br>
   <p style="text-align: initial"><strong>Note</strong>: This website is still in active development and constantly changing!  If you have any issues or suggestions, please contact me at: alex.aguirre0026@gmail.com</p> 
   </br> 

